Extended Hours: Friday and Saturday: 10 am–9 pm

Closed: Wednesday

Closed Thanksgiving Day, December 25, January 1, and the first Monday in May.

Hours: Thursday–Tuesday: 10 am–5 pm

Closed: Wednesday

Closed Thanksgiving Day, December 25, and January 1.

![The Met's Michael C. Rockefeller Wing](https://cdn.sanity.io/images/cctd4ker/production/d3b5f5fd37cefc18b7937075bd8943a65935f2fe-8192x5464.jpg?rect=0,694,8192,4617&w=3840&q=75&fit=clip&auto=format)

### The Michael C. Rockefeller Wing

Now open! Discover The Met’s new Michael C. Rockefeller Wing, featuring the Museum’s collections of the Arts of Africa, the Ancient Americas, and Oceania.

[Learn more](/hubs/the-michael-c-rockefeller-wing)

![A group of people on The Met's Cantor Roof Garden](https://cdn.sanity.io/images/cctd4ker/production/862fa16271a828df7ba1181ef12e69d7f055fced-5120x2880.jpg?w=3840&q=75&fit=clip&auto=format)

### Summer at The Met

Escape the heat in our galleries, dive into free tours, special programs, and more.

[Learn more](https://www.metmuseum.org/hubs/summer-at-the-met)

![A man and woman walking in The Met's Astor Court.](https://cdn.sanity.io/images/cctd4ker/production/8e75e498fbe5003476b9c8b946fa9120e2ce113c-5221x3481.jpg?rect=0,537,5221,2944&w=3840&q=75&fit=clip&auto=format)

### Become a Member

Discover more of The Met as a Member. Join today to enjoy free admission, Preview Days for new exhibitions, special events, and much more.

[Join now](https://engage.metmuseum.org/members/membership/?promocode=60367)

![A woman in a patterned caftan.](https://cdn.sanity.io/images/cctd4ker/production/b62721cea21b494d75f78c3f10fb73cc51ca41db-1920x1090.jpg?rect=0,0,1920,1082&w=3840&q=75&fit=clip&auto=format)

### Summer Essentials

Take The Met with you wherever you go this summer with lively designs inspired by the Museum’s holdings.

[Shop The Met Store](https://store.metmuseum.org/?utm_source=mainmuseum&utm_medium=metmuseum.org&utm_campaign=012725-locket-jewelry)
